Title: Data and Server Management for a Distributed Workflow System  
Author: Mark D. Spiller and L. Kristin Wright 
Date: May 16, 1997  
Abstract: This paper describes a workflow design that addresses current research areas in workflow systems. The specific type of workflow we design for is a CAD Design workflow. However, we believe our resulting architecture is suitable for general work-flows models. 
